{"tid":322440,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖)電腦冇左睡眠模式用","createTime":"2017-07-14T20:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T04:43:25.000Z","uid":8232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d3bb07fe96921f3b1f1cb757f2bff15229098420","tid":322440,"uid":8232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T20:45:25.000Z","msg":"小弟最近update左ryzen chipset driver 用埋佢個ryzen balanced power mode <br />\n但第二日開機發現bios都讀唔到隻hdd 靜係讀到ssd<br />\n所以我就重新裝過driver 同 唔用佢個ryzen balanced power mode <br />\n就解決左hdd個問題<br />\n<br />\n但之後發覺唔見左睡眠模式個option 點較都較唔返出黎 bios 都reset過default setting同update過 都洗過機 差在未clear cmos <br />\n依家情況就咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/044407_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F044407_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=e2784460&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/044407_671b694133bcab38ffccd755c4e06c90.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F044407_671b694133bcab38ffccd755c4e06c90.png&h=382561d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/044407_0e48589c214b7bbac9c5ea2a43f55470.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F044407_0e48589c214b7bbac9c5ea2a43f55470.png&h=080ce941&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問可以點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de880eed0893fff0f59b742f387bfb8b2b12932","tid":322440,"uid":8232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T20:46:28.000Z","msg":"ryzen balanced power plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79707e0150c3816c6101544b1240db22bb36205","tid":322440,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"